title: 08/23/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 08/23/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP and the guys return from vacation to recap what's happened in NFL preseason thus far. Peter King Explains which Rookie QBs have stood out most. DP shares some information he received about College Football over the break. And Andy Staples discusses the time frame of when The Alliance, Big 10, Pac 12 and ACC, will join forces.
